---
title: Chorizo Linguine in Creamy Sauce with Peas, Rocket and Balsamic Glaze
description: This Chorizo Linguine in Creamy Sauce is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W09_UK_G11648-13273-3_Main_low-9422edd4.jpg
